scripts.allure:clean: rm -r allure-results/ allure-report cypress/screenshots cypress/videos || true
scripts.allure:history: mv -f allure-report/history allure-report/history && rm -r allure-report || true
scripts.cypress: npm run allure:clean && npx cypress run --browser electron --spec cypress/e2e/test/test.spec.cy.ts --env allure=true && npm run allure:report
